3ï¸âƒ£ Diagnostic Annotation System
ğŸ”¹ Where? EBRAINS Lab & Neurodiagnoses Web Platform
ğŸ”¹ What Happens?

AI generates two diagnostic reports per case:
1ï¸âƒ£ Probabilistic Diagnosis (traditional classification with probabilities).
2ï¸âƒ£ Tridimensional Diagnosis (classification based on etiology, biomarkers, and neuroanatomical correlation).
Results are annotated with SHAP interpretability tools.
